{"tid":1780332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"王國興亡在此一票？4年3連戰，極端多變的「2019英國大選」","createTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T01:50:07.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"857f69fdf85c4edea86d071a93fa1f151b0226e3","tid":1780332,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/12/12/99/7185382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F99%2F7185382.jpg&h=83c04289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12日是2019英國國會大選的全國投票日，從當地時間上午7點開始至晚間10點為止...<br />\n<br />\n王國興亡在此一票？4年3連戰，極端多變的「2019英國大選」<br />\n<br />\n「4年來的第3次大選，能幫英國指出『脫歐明路』嗎？」12日是2019英國國會大選的全國投票日，從當地時間上午7點開始至晚間10點為止，全英選民將選出650席國會下議院席次、並藉此決定「後脫歐時代」的下一任內閣與首相人選。根據選前的最後民調，始終領先、但個人聲望極差的現任首相強生（Boris Johnson），頗有機會帶領保守黨贏得「絕對過半」的優勢席次；但極獲年輕進步派肯定，卻因「激進復古社會主義」而被認為是「英國40年來最不受歡迎的在野黨領袖」的工黨黨魁柯賓（Jeremy Corbyn），則相信一向消極難以預測的年輕選民能夠出來投票，並配合留歐派選民鼓吹的「戰術性棄保」，進而逆轉這場決定「英國國家軸心」的宿命選戰。"},{"pid":"032f843006945bc11bb05ce2298f1893f4f42be1","tid":1780332,"uid":550,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯王國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be821da1543d0b22f664d7c1794aefb9bde78a21","tid":1780332,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"在本回的大選中，英國必須選出650席區域議員，其中席次第一大黨將被優先授權組閣。若有政黨能贏得326席國會過半，則能直接組成多數內閣；但若沒有政黨能取得過半，議會則將進入「懸峙議會」，兩大黨必須斡旋談判組成聯合內閣或少數內閣，否則就得再度重新大選。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國民調機構YouGov在選前當周所公布的最終民調，強生所領導的保守黨目前以43%的支持度，穩居第一大黨；但在過去10天內，強生之於工黨柯賓的領先優勢，卻於倒數階段劇烈縮減，雙方的民調差距也從雙位數領先、落到只剩個位數的9%&mdash;&mdash;甚至在部分分析中，保守黨與工黨的差距，可能已於選前48小時進入「接近平手」的誤差距離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/global.udn.com/global_vision/amp/story/8662/4221521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Famp%2Fstory%2F8662%2F4221521&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fcx5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=98f28962\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/global.udn.com/global_vision/amp/story/8662/4221521</a>"},{"pid":"8d9c2314783599f96abc007aeeec425b49211c31","tid":1780332,"uid":86027,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"睇左王國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19a1ae28d26a907c19376bedb41cacc43b7bc33","tid":1780332,"uid":253945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"032f843006945bc11bb05ce2298f1893f4f42be1","tid":1780332,"uid":550,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯王國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8959fa30b0435669b56156008abcd0b8a6ef8fe","tid":1780332,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"032f843006945bc11bb05ce2298f1893f4f42be1","tid":1780332,"uid":550,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯王國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"瘋狂寫大字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cc7d2ba32f4c3bb998b9c15e783583eabdc480","tid":1780332,"uid":46155,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"諗緊關王國興咩事..."},{"pid":"970cd21d1ea50de24a73aaa2e5561c215aa73296","tid":1780332,"uid":13914,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"樓主標題好撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n王國興 亡在此一票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全好奇禁入黎睇點亡"},{"pid":"7cd38563ba70e4009ec00f12a151110166043b84","tid":1780332,"uid":28114,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"馬國明放假一天，王國興亡在一票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cae811bdc6be4490b25cd44aea561d7ed906b35","tid":1780332,"uid":55583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b19a1ae28d26a907c19376bedb41cacc43b7bc33","tid":1780332,"uid":253945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"032f843006945bc11bb05ce2298f1893f4f42be1","tid":1780332,"uid":550,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯王國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"我仲諗緊王國興關英國大選咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea082a095581f7c3a1ad06512268eeac461234cb","tid":1780332,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"哥賓 好撚乞人憎"},{"pid":"d926be13531f610adacbcff3e1de33ff4da6f80c","tid":1780332,"uid":43809,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbNH5sN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbNH5sN.jpg&h=abc17488&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b68674f830c4a60e99661e3b042c18ec1c2abcb2","tid":1780332,"uid":98993,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"171162368c54faefba2015a9d5da43f8b64cfa59","tid":1780332,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"032f843006945bc11bb05ce2298f1893f4f42be1","tid":1780332,"uid":550,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯王國興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/n